          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the broccoli is almost done, remove the <strong>tomato</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> and transfer straight to a <strong>food processor</strong></p>\n<p>Leave the <strong>Tenderstem</strong> <strong>broccoli</strong> on the tray </p>\n<p>Add the <strong>flaked</strong> <strong>almonds</strong> to the baking tray and return the tray to the oven for 5 min further</p>",
